"535":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-21","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"预约海边网球场 1 号场，2026 年 4 月 2 日 19:00-20:00 的包场预约"},"536":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-22","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"预约海边网球场 2 号场，2026 年 4 月 2 日 19:00-20:00 的包场预约（如果上一步的 1 号场预约成功，将会提示无法购票，属于合理预期情况）"},"537":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-23","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"预约海边网球场 1 号场，2026 年 4 月 2 日 20:00-21:00 的包场预约"},"538":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-24","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"预约海边网球场 2 号场，2026 年 4 月 2 日 20:00-21:00 的包场预约（与上述同理）"},"539":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-25","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"`stuid` 是学号，脚本会根据它来获取对应的预约人信息，并将预约结果关联到这个人上。示例中的 `2025101011` 是项目作者的学号，我们需要替换成自己的学号。"},"540":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-26","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"`stuname` 是姓名。示例中的 `张三` 是一个虚拟的姓名，我们需要替换成自己的姓名。"},"541":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-27","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"`cookies` 是登录后获取到的 Cookie 字符串，脚本会使用它来模拟登录状态，向预约接口发起请求。由于 Cookie 的有效期通常只有 3\\~4 小时，建议在抢票前半小时内重新登录并获取最新 Cookie，以确保脚本能正常工作。"},"542":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-28","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#4-运行脚本","content":"运行成功后，它将会返回类似下面的输出："},"543":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-29","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"总结一下，我们要做的事情就是："},"544":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-30","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"**检查环境**：确保网络代理和必要的软件（Git、Python）已正确安装和配置"},"545":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-31","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"**获取源码并安装依赖**：从 GitHub 克隆项目，创建虚拟环境，并安装所需的 Python 库"},"546":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-32","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"**配置购票参数**：根据目标场馆和项目，修改脚本中的参数（`courses`、`stuid`、`stuname`、`cookies`）以匹配准备预约的时间和场地"},"547":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-33","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"**运行脚本**：执行 Python 脚本，让它自动完成购票流程"},"548":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-34","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#常见问题","content":"由于不需要处理界面，只需要向目标接口发起网络请求，因此速度更快，效率更高。但行为特征较明显，服务器更容易识别为自动化操作。\n不过这类相对不重要的校园系统通常不会特别严格地防护。"},"549":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-35","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#常见问题","content":"Cookie 的有效期通常只有 3\\~4 小时。建议在抢票前半小时内重新登录并获取最新 Cookie，以确保脚本能正常工作。"},"550":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-36","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#继续探索","content":"用 Playwright 自动打开浏览器并登录，用于获取 Cookie"},"551":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-37","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#继续探索","content":"用「任务计划程序」定时运行脚本（图形化界面 或 命令行界面）"},"552":{"id":"/docs/discord/betterdiscord","page_id":"/docs/discord/betterdiscord","type":"page","content":"BetterDiscord","tags":[],"url":"/docs/discord/betterdiscord"},"553":{"id":"/docs/discord/betterdiscord-0","page_id":"/docs/discord/betterdiscord","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/discord/betterdiscord","content":"https\\://betterdiscord.app/"},"554":{"id":"/docs/discord/betterdiscord-1","page_id"